snippet.title: Ep 59: Eating Keto to Control Diabetes - Amber Wentworth, Lone Star Keto Girl, MeatRx Coach
snippet.description:
Have you tried almost every diet in the book and still fail to keep the weight off? Amber Wentworth, Meat RX nutritional coach, has been there too! After years upon years of struggling with her weight, Amber eventually stumbled upon the ketogenic diet and immediately experienced life-changing results which made her scream, "Why haven't I heard of this before?!" 

In this epic episode of Health Solutions with Shawn & Janet Needham, live show & podcast...

You'll Learn:
• What makes the keto diet so special
• How to lose AND maintain weight
• How keto can work wonders with diabetics
• Why fruits and grains should be eaten in moderation
• Why the carnivore diet is anti-inflammatory & is a better alternative to Nexium

~
